Text: I thought that this torrent due to its unusual nature and Wood being a cult figure as an award winning turkey, would support itself after a few hours like my other ones here. That didnt happen, so I must leave it to itself now, I hope others will keep it alive. Cheers.
Thank you for keeping it alive, its funny, isnt it? Poor Ed, he tried but was happily unaware of his basic incompetence... How THAT can become a cult thing, its a sad witness to our time...
